  <md:title>Who Are the Elderly? Aging in Society</md:title>
  <md:abstract><list>
<item>Understand the difference between senior age groups (young-old, middle-old, and old-old)</item>
<item>Describe the “graying of the United States” as the population experiences increased life expectancies</item>
<item>Examine aging as a global issue</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:uuid>6ab47917-4d79-4006-9d6e-b5a4b9ed0187</md:uuid>
